 '2025-10-01 08:06:17.653201+00', '2026-01-08 13:06:47.625214+00', 'true', '120', 'size'), ('f63e2eec-a8e1-4409-ac5e-57c0295bf77e', 'YOPOKKI ROSE', 'Chewy rice cakes drenched in a creamy, mildly spicy rose sauce — a rich and flavorful twist on a Korean favorite.', '135.00', 'diy-korean-ramen', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756733585342-kn6yrcnsem.webp', '2025-09-01 13:33:08.976416+00', '2026-01-08 13:06:47.625214+00', 'false', '107', 'size'), ('f6bbe85f-09c6-43aa-9e30-66e57cf8e8e0', 'ULTIMATE CRISPY PATA', 'A golden-fried pork knuckle with irresistibly crunchy skin and tender, juicy meat inside. Perfectly seasoned and cooked to perfection, served fresh for sharing — a true comfort feast that brings bold flavor and satisfying crunch in every bite.', '595.00', 'ala-carte', 'true', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1769844099031-971mmz678l.jpeg', '2026-01-31 07:05:06.412539+00', '2026-02-18 04:48:06.933986+00', 'true', '1', 'size'), ('f7a102c3-3460-4597-be46-1d275192a74d', 'ESPRESSO CRAVE FRAPPE', 'Our Espresso Crave Frappe is a smooth blend of bold espresso, creamy milk, and ice—crafted to deliver a rich coffee punch wrapped in a refreshing chill. A perfect treat for those who love their coffee strong, cold, and irresistibly smooth.', '180.00', 'frappe-and-shakes', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1765180574139-e4ly71cuorn.png', '2025-11-20 13:45:34.465322+00', '2026-02-10 06:13:04.517371+00', 'true', '15', 'size'), ('f83c087a-9cad-4608-ba72-2d5c12cb496a', 'DARK CHOCOLATE FRAPPE', 'Bold meets indulgent in this rich blend of dark chocolate and freshly brewed coffee, perfectly chilled and blended into a creamy, energizing treat. Finished with whipped cream and a drizzle of decaden.', '180.00', 'frappe-and-shakes', 'true', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1765180055172-b0gmm366upi.png', '2025-09-01 11:39:06.914823+00', '2026-02-15 12:14:24.63168+00', 'true', '12', 'size'), ('f95eb42e-0888-4f36-87a4-1ed2ca375d11', 'ICED SEA SALT MATCHA', 'A harmony of umami matcha and sea salt cream - bold smooth and satisfying', '170.00', 'matcha-special', 'true', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1771596976827-oxxxof4oeak.jpeg', '2025-09-05 09:52:14.878204+00', '2026-02-20 14:16:30.762863+00', 'true', '109', 'size'), ('fa0c5680-f17c-49fa-812e-f309fca6bd0f', 'SANSRIVAL ALMOND', 'A decadent Filipino dessert featuring layers of buttery almond meringue and rich buttercream, creating a perfect balance of crunch and creamy sweetness. A true indulgence for almond lovers!', '150.00', 'cakes', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756731663427-vceg5eiqtv.jpg', '2025-08-30 06:43:05.990222+00', '2026-02-20 07:14:13.676784+00', 'true', '7', 'size'), ('fbb0433b-7329-4af1-93f9-96ed1dc4f560', 'SHIN STIR FRY', 'Chewy noodles tossed in Shin Ramyun’s signature spicy sauce — a quick and flavorful stir-fry with a bold, fiery kick.', '100.00', 'diy-korean-ramen', 'false', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1756733469691-4q1xzzjpazr.webp', '2025-09-01 13:31:14.769194+00', '2026-02-06 04:07:09.830435+00', 'false', '105', 'size'), ('fd209790-f76f-46f9-9f52-131469b774ce', 'ICED BISCOFF LATTE', 'A creamy latte blended with rich Biscoff cookie butter and smooth espresso, topped with frothy milk and biscoff crunch. Perfectly indulgent and comforting.', '210.00', 'iced-coffee', 'true', 'https://xnnracrkpapdfqcistvh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/menu-images/1771721239157-4zto0gx47z5.jpeg', '2025-09-01 11:03:30.437355+00', '2026-02-22 00:47:27.735012+00', 'true', '5', 'size') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

